tools.timestamp-guesser.title: Timestamp Format Guesser
tools.timestamp-guesser.description: Auto-detect timestamp formats: seconds, milliseconds, microseconds, nanoseconds, Excel, LDAP, etc.
tools.timestamp-guesser.inputHint: Supports multiple formats: Unix seconds/ms/Î¼s/ns, Excel date, LDAP/FILETIME, etc.
tools.timestamp-guesser.toolInfo: Different systems and applications use different timestamp formats. Unix timestamps use 1970-01-01 as epoch, Excel uses 1899-12-30, and LDAP/Windows FILETIME uses 1601-01-01. This tool helps identify what time format an unknown numeric value might represent.
